James Thornton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Thornton_(actor) 0 James Thornton (born 31 October 1975) is an English actor and voice-over artist. He is best known for portraying John Barton on the long-running British soap opera Emmerdale from 2009 to 2012. He has been acting since 1997.
